<br>
Increased Double Attack - Increases our chance of getting two swings.<br>
<br>
Bane Undead - Gives us a damage bonus when using any weapon versus undead.  Gives different bonuses with 1-handers and 2-handers.<br>
<br>
Resist Fear Buff - A group buff that increases everyone's Fear resistance.<br>
<br>
Rage of the Righteous - Every swing for the next 10 seconds hits for maximum damage.<br>
<br>
As you can see from these, I think we are in good shape defensively and from a spell casting point of view.  We need more melee damage output.<br>
